  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<h1 class=\"title\"><img src=\"modules/pf-content/assets/PathfinderSocietySymbol.gif\" style=\"margin:3px 3px 0px 3px;\" title=\"PFS Legal\"/> Bottled lightning</h1><b>Source</b> <i>Ultimate Equipment pg. 107</i><br/><b>Price</b> 40 gp; <b>Weight</b> 1 lb.<br/><b>Category</b> Alchemical Weapons<h2 class=\"framing\">Description</h2><p>Electricity crackles along a metal filament inside this small glass bottle. You can open the bottle as a standard action, unleashing a small bolt of lightning toward an enemy within 20 feet of you. This is a ranged touch attack that deals 1d8 points of electricity damage. Any creature in a line between you and the target (including the target) takes 1 point of sonic damage from the terrific clap of thunder the bolt generates (Reflex DC 15 negates). Crafting bottled lightning is a DC 25 Craft (alchemy) check.</p><h2 class=\"framing\">Construction</h2><p><b>Craft (Alchemy)</b> DC 25</p>",
